ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The class is an opportunity to learn about our classmates research. I would recommend this class to other students because it is important to learn to communicate your science to others and to learn about other fields.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class forced me to present my work as a coherent story which is great preparation for committee meetings.
helps keep up-to-date of current researches going on in the department, some of which are quite intriguing. quite helpful for my own research
